```{r}
Seatbelts_data = data.frame(as.matrix(Seatbelts),date=time(Seatbelts))

ggplot(data=Seatbelts_data, aes(x=date,y=DriversKilled,col=law))+geom_line()
ggplot(data=Seatbelts_data, aes(x=date,y=front,col=law))+geom_line()
ggplot(data=Seatbelts_data, aes(x=date,y=rear,col=law))+geom_line()
```
